# Title: Potential Amazon SSM Agent Hijacking
# Author: Muhammad Faisal
# Date: 2023-08-02
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects potential Amazon SSM agent hijack attempts as outlined in the Mitiga research report.
# MITRE Tactic: Command and Control
# Tags: attack.command-and-control, attack.persistence, attack.t1219.002
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_ssm_agent_abuse.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate activity of system administrators

CommandLine="*-register *" CommandLine="*-code *" CommandLine="*-id *" CommandLine="*-region *" Image="*\\amazon-ssm-agent.exe"